# Dashboard Page Requirements

- Enforce dynamic role-based rendering views on components:
  - **Student View:** Show Assignment & Student Progress modules (Read-Only)
  - **Faculty View:** Show Assignment & Student Progress management controls
  - **Admin View:** Show User Management panel with full CRUD capabilities
- Ensure clean layout structures to completely eliminate component content shifts.
